Collection of C++ and Python functional tests for BornAgain libraries

Tests are compiled and executed automatically when the whole project
is build with 'check' target:
  cmake; make check

Content:
  ./TestCore    - C++ tests of libBornAgainCore library using variety of scattering geometries and experimental settings
  ./TestPyCore  - same for Python
  ./TestFit     - C++ tests of libBornAgainFit library using different fitting strategies
  ./TestPyFit   - same for Python
  ./TestGUI     - testing of GUI functionality on model side

See also:
  http://apps.jcns.fz-juelich.de/redmine/projects/bornagain/wiki/Creation_of_new_functional_test
